    "Id": 7,
    "Content": "\n## Usage\n\nAll input data including key, IV, plaintext and ciphertext should be a `String` or `ArrayBuffer` / `Buffer`.\nStrings support all unicode including emoji ✨.\n\n### Example\n",
    "ContentSha": "tB2dShdyDuOx1fWX6xyGBK5R5SXpSvshDlp0y+sN87k=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
